"menu.engine.howto" = "How to Choose an Engine";
"engine.howto.message" = "• Apple Speech\nBest for: free, built-in dictation, broad language coverage, and low setup cost.\nWhat changed: it remains the default general-purpose engine. It needs no API key, supports fast streaming results, and can use Apple Force Offline for supported languages when the local speech asset is installed.\nTradeoffs: many languages still use Apple's online service by default; weak networks or Apple service issues can affect reliability. Forced offline mode may be unavailable or less accurate.\n\n• Sherpa Local Recognition\nBest for: privacy-first use, offline work, and avoiding cloud audio processing.\nWhat changed: the app now supports model presets by current language and can download the runtime, ASR model, and punctuation model from Recognition Engine Settings. Audio stays on this Mac.\nTradeoffs: first setup downloads large model files; larger presets use more disk, memory, and startup time. Current local models may be weaker with long sentences, mixed languages, punctuation, and proper nouns.\n\n• Doubao Cloud ASR\nBest for: Mandarin Chinese accuracy, low-latency streaming, and cloud ASR features such as ITN, disfluency cleanup, punctuation, and second-pass refinement.\nWhat changed: configure API Key, Resource ID, and Endpoint in Doubao/ASR settings. Language, auto punctuation, and stop delay follow the main menu; credentials are stored in Keychain.\nTradeoffs: microphone audio is sent to Volcengine/Doubao, requires a stable network, and may incur usage costs on your Volcengine account.\n\n• LLM Text Refinement\nNote: this is not a recognition engine. It runs after ASR to fix misheard words, homophones, punctuation, names, and formatting. The recognized text is sent to your selected LLM provider; audio is not sent.\n\nRecommendation: choose Doubao for best Chinese accuracy; Sherpa for privacy and fully offline use; Apple for free, general, multilingual dictation; Apple Force Offline only when you want Apple Speech to stay local as much as possible.";

